    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>The Ingratiator</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>John Kucera letter on James Traub's July 30 article on Rick Lazio holds one about Hillary Clinton should be called 'The Prevaricator'</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Regarding your title for the article on Rick Lazio: I look forward to reading an article on Hillary Clinton called ''The Prevaricator.''</p>
        <p>John Kucera  Boyne City, Mich.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>Regarding your title for the article on Rick Lazio: I look forward to reading an article on Hillary Clinton called ''The Prevaricator.''</p>
